This is just a collection of basic scripts and utilities I use for manipulating
data and running various experiments.

htk/
Contains scripts for manipulating data created by the Hidden Markov Model 
Toolkit (HTK).

math/
Scripts that perform various mathematical functions, mostly on text files.

oneoff/
Scripts that are highly specialized to a particular situation. They are unlikely
to be used in the future, but pieces of them might be of use.

stk/
Scripts for modifying data and running the various utilities of the STK, a 
proprietary toolkit used at LIMSI-CNRS

string_manipulation
Scripts that operate or manipulate strings or files containing lists of strings.
